اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011120, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Knower of the unseen and the secrets. O the all-Knowing. O Allah, O Allah, O Allah. O One who defeated the allies for Muhammad blessings of Allah be on him and his family. O One who plotted against Firaun for Musa (a). O One who saved Isa (a) from darkness. O One who saved the people of Nuh (a) from drowning. O One who was merciful to His servant Ya’qub O One who removed the distress from Ayyub.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay ghaibat aur raazo’n ke jaanne waale, ay mere daana (hikmato’n waala) Ma’bood, ay Allah, ay Allah, ay Allah! Ay Paighambar'e Akram (s.a.w.a) ke dushmano ko mutafarriq karne (bikher-ne) waale, ay Moosa (a.s) ke liye Firaun ko fareb dene waale, aur Eesa (a.s) ko taareeki se najaat dene waale, ay qaum'e Nuh (a.s) ko garq hone (doobh ne) se bachaane waale, ay apne bande Yaqoob (a.s) par rahem karne waale, ay Ayyoob (a.s) se mushkilaat dur karne waale.", "Urdu": "اے غیب اور رازوں کے جاننے والے، اے میرے دانا معبود، یا اللہ، یا اللہ، یا اللہ اے پیغمبر اکرم کے دشمنوں کو متفرق کرنے والے، اے موسیٰ کے لئے فرعون کو فریب دینے والے، اور عیسیٰ کو تاریکی سے نجات دینے والے، اے قوم نوح کو غرق ہونے سے بچانے والے، اے اپنے بندے یعقوب پر رحم کرنے والے، اے ایوب سے مشکلات دور کرنے والے۔", "RArabic": "YAA A’ALEMAL GHAYBE WAS SARAA-ERE, YAA MOTAA-O’ YAA A’LEEMO, YAA ALLAAHO YAA ALLAAHO YAA ALLAAHO YAA HAAZEMAL AHZAABE LE-MOHAMMADIN SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHI, YAA KAA-EDA FIR-A’WNA LE-MOOSAA, YAA MUNJEYA E’ESAA MIN AYDIZ ZALAMATE, YAA MOKHALLESA QAWME NOOHIN MENAL GHARAQE, YAA RAAHEMA A'BDE’I YA’QOOBA YAA KAASHEFA ZURRE AYYOOBA.", "ArabicText1": "یَا عَالِمَ الْغَیْبِ وَالسَّرَاۗءِرِ، یَا مُطَاعُ یَا عَلِیْمُ، یَا اَللهُ یَا اَللهُ یَا اَللهُ، یَاهَازِمَ الْاَحَزَابِ لِمُحَمَّدٍ صَلَّی اللهُ عَلَیْهِ وَآلِهٖ، یَا كَاۗءِدَ فِرْعَوْنَ لِمُوْسٰی، یَا مُنْجِیَ عِیْسٰی مِنَ اَیْدِی الظَّالَمَۃِ، یَا مُخَلِّصَ قَوْمِ نُوْحٍ مِنَ الْغَرَقِ، یَا رَاحِمَ عَبْدِهٖ یَعْقُوْبَ، یَا كَاشِفَ ضُرِّ اَیُوْبَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011121, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O One who saved Yunus form the darkness. O One who does all good. O One who guides towards all good. O One who shows all that is good. O One who orders towards all good. O One who created good. O One who possesses all good. You are Allah. I hope from You all that You already know and You are the Knower of the unseen. I beseech You to bless Muhammad and his family.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Hazrat Yoonus (a.s) ko taareekiyo’n (machhlee ke peyt) se najaat dene waale, ay har neyki karne waale, aur har achchhaayi ki taraf hidaayat karne waale, aur tamaam achchhaaiyo’n par rehnumaayi karne waale, ay har neyki ka hukm dene waale, ay har achchhaayi ke paiyda karne waale, ay neykiyo’n waale, Tu mera Ma’bood hai keh mai Teri taraf raaghib hu (rujhaan hai), yaqeenan Tu jaanta hai aur Tu hai raazo’n se aagaah, Tujh se sawaal karti hu keh Tu Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par durood bhej.", "Urdu": "اے حضرت یونس کو تاریکیوں سے نجات دینے والے، اے ہر نیکی کرنے والے، اور ہر اچھائی کی طرف ہدایت کرنے والے اور تمام اچھائیوں پر راہنمائی کرنے والے، اے ہر نیکی کا حکم دینے والے، اے ہر اچھائی کے پیدا کرنے والے، اے نیکیوں والے، تو میرا معبود ہے، جس سے میں تیری طرف راغب ہوں یقینًا تو جانتا ہے اور تو ہے رازوں سے آگاہ، تجھ سے سوال کرتی ہوں کہ تو محمد و آل پر درود بھیج۔", "RArabic": "YAA MUNJEYA ZEEN NOONE MENAZ ZOLOMAATE, YAA FAA-E’LA KULLE KHAYRIN, YAA HAADEYAN ELAA KULLE KHAYRIN, YAA DAAL-LAN A’LAA KULLE KHAYRIN, YAA AAMERAN BE-KULLE KHAYRIN, YAA KHAALEQAL KHAYRE, WA YAA AHLAL KHAYRE, ANTAL LAAHO RA-GHIBTO ELAYKA FEEMAA QAD A’LIMTA WA ANTA A’LLAAMUL GHOYOOBE, AS-ALOKA AN TOSALLEYA A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN.", "ArabicText1": "یَا مُنْجِیَ ذِی النَّوْنِ مِنَ الظُّلُمَاتِ، یَا فَاعِلَ كُلِّ خَیْرٍ، یَا هَادِیًا اِلٰی كُلِّ خَیْرٍ، یَا دَالًا عَلٰی كُلِّ خَیْرٍ، یَا آمِرًا بِكُلِّ خَیْرٍ، یَا خَالِقَ الْخَیْرِ، وَیَا اَهْلَ الْخَیْرِ، اَنْتَ اللهُ رَغِبْتُ اِلَیْكَ فِیْمَا قَدْ عَلِمْتَ وَاَنْتَ عَلَّامُ الْغُیُوْبِ، اَسْئَلُكَ اَنْ تُصَلِّیَ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14"